    <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="Body-investigation-hanging">Is the statement below
    true both for prisms and pyramids?</p>
    
   
    <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="Body-investigation-hanging">the number of faces + the
    number of vertices = 2 + the number of edges</p>
    
     <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="aside">
      <p class="Body-box-no-indent"><span>This statement is
      called</span> <b>Euler's
      formula</b> <span>for polyhedra.</span></p>
    </div>
    
